- **Live in:** `.claude/skills/refine/SKILL.md` ‚Äî ¬ß0.2 tier table
- **Current:**

  | Tier | Autonomy | Approval | Planning model |
  |------|----------|----------|----------------|
  | small | fully-autonomous ‚Äî no questions | auto-accept | sonnet |
  | medium | key-questions-only ‚Äî 1‚Äì3 questions | auto-accept | session-model |
  | large | many-questions ‚Äî interview mode | manual-approval | opus |

- **Options:** autonomy ‚àà {fully-autonomous, key-questions-only, many-questions} ¬∑ approval ‚àà {auto-accept, manual-approval} ¬∑ model ‚àà {session-model, sonnet, opus, haiku, fable}
- **Note:** the tier is assessed automatically and applied without asking; you are only consulted on sizing if you explicitly ask to be. In unsupervised mode no questions are asked at any tier and specs are self-approved.

